ec.app.aspga

Class DayPlanGene

  • java.lang.Object
    • ec.vector.Gene
      • ec.app.aspga.DayPlanGene
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ec.Prototype, ec.Setup, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class DayPlanGene
extends ec.vector.Gene
    The Gene that represent the individual genome.
    In this class is implemented the mutation logic, the creation of the initial population and the method used to compare two individuals.
